  "texts": [
    "Therefore, ISAC has become a popular research area, attracting significant research interest from both academia and industry.Despite the commonalities mentioned above, radar and communications follow different principles and serve fundamentally different purposes.",
    "The primary functionality of radar is target detection and parameter estimation [25].",
    "Specifically, it transmits the deterministic signal and analyses the echo reflected by the target to determine its critical information, such as distance, speed, and angle, thus enabling accurate identification and tracking [26].",
    "The communication system, on the other hand, aims at effective message delivery, prioritizing high-speed and high-reliability transmission [26] and reliable transmission [27].",
    "The base station (BS) transmits the modulated signal with a high degree of randomness and the users decode the received signal, often contaminated by noise and interference, by means of various advanced demodulation techniques [28]."
  ],
